title: Bug 109350 - Output parameter not displaying in data set dialog
description: The output parameter is not appearing in the data set dialog on the query result page.
OB: While in the query result page, no data is returned. The actual result is that the output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
EB: When on the query result page, the output parameter should be visible in the edit data set dialog.
SR:
1. Navigate to the query result page.
2. Observe that no data is returned.
3. Expected behavior: The output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
